text: Gabriela Krčmářová (born 16 March 1978) is a Czech gymnast. She competed in five events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Czech female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the Czech Republic Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from Karviná
